<title>USA: Harte-Hanks names Jacques Kerrest CFO.</title>
<headline>Harte-Hanks names Jacques Kerrest CFO.</headline>
<dateline>SAN ANTONIO, Texas 1997-07-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Harte-Hanks Communications Inc said Monday it named Jacques Kerrest as senior vice president and chief financial officer.</p>
<p>Kerrest was most recently chief financial officer of Chancellor Broadcasting Co in Dallas, Harte-Hanks said.  </p>
<p>Kerrest replaces Dick Ritchie in both positions.  Ritchie left the company last year.</p>
